OL,3,CUK retail sales remained flat as wet
OL,4,Cweather dampens food shopping
OL,6,FUK retail sales remained flat in
OL,7,FFebruary as food and fuel sellers saw
OL,8,Fa decline during the month, according
OL,9,Fto data from the Office for National
OL,10,FStatistics (ONS).
OL,12,FSales showed growth of 0.0% in
OL,13,FFebruary, down from the month before,
OL,14,Fthe ONS said.
OL,16,FOnline sales had grown during the
OL,17,Fmonth, especially for clothing, as
OL,18,Flast month's wet weather pushed down
OL,19,Fthe footfall of people heading out to
OL,20,Fthe shops.
