OL,3,CUK retail sales remained flat as wet
OL,4,Cweather dampens food shopping
OL,6,FThe ONS said a "mild but wet" month
OL,7,Fwhere southern England saw its wettest
OL,8,FFebruary on record had helped to weigh
OL,9,Fon sales.
OL,11,FFood shops saw their sales drop by
OL,12,F0.3% during the month, with those who
OL,13,Fresponded to the ONS survey blaming
OL,14,Fthe weather for reducing the number of
OL,15,Fpeople visiting the shops.
