OL,3,CUK retail sales remained flat as wet
OL,4,Cweather dampens food shopping
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the amount spent online,
OL,7,Fespecially on clothes, rose 2.1%
OL,8,Fduring the month, the largest single
OL,9,Frise since July, when poor weather was
OL,10,Falso to thank.
OL,12,FONS Senior Statistician Heather Bovill
OL,13,Fsaid: "Retail sales were flat in
OL,14,FFebruary. There was growth in
OL,15,Fclothing, which rebounded after recent
OL,16,Ffalls as people invested in the new
OL,17,Fseason's collections, as well as
OL,18,Fdepartment stores.
