OL,4,Cweather dampens food shopping
OL,6,FLisa Hooker, leader of industry for
OL,7,Fconsumer markets at the PwC
OL,8,Fconsultancy, said: "Little surprise
OL,9,Fthat retail sales were unable to
OL,10,Fcontinue the momentum of the apparent
OL,11,Fbounceback witnessed in January's
OL,12,Fnumbers following a lacklustre
OL,13,FChristmas."
OL,15,FShe added: "Grocery sales slowed
OL,16,Fslightly from the previous month's
OL,17,Fhighs, as more people ventured back to
OL,18,Feating and drinking out after Dry
OL,19,FJanuary.
