OL,6,F"Overall, February's retail sales
OL,7,Ffigures confirm that, despite falling
OL,8,Finflation, a 2% cut in national
OL,9,Finsurance at the start of 2024, and
OL,10,Fimproving consumer confidence in their
OL,11,Fpersonal finances, shoppers are still
OL,12,Fhesitant to part with their hard-
OL,13,Fearned cash."
